    "The data are kindly provided by research partners within the research unit FOR 2895 [21].",
    "A detailed description of the numerical setup is presented in [13,14].",
    "The leading airfoil within the tandem configuration is a supercritical ONERA OAT15A with chord length c front = 0.15 m at an angle of attack of 5 •, whereas the rear airfoil is a NACA64A110 with chord length crear = 0.075 m placed at a horizontal distance of 2c front behind the leading airfoil's trailing edge.",
    "The inflow Mach number is M a∞ = 0.72, leading to a freestream Reynolds number of Re∞ = 2 • 10 6 based on the chord length of the leading airfoil.",
    "Under these conditions, the leading airfoil exhibits periodic shock-boundary layer interactions known as shock buffet."
